{"tid":1880746,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博：廁紙成香港貨幣","createTime":"2020-02-15T05:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T06:02:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"412ce7505c309f5b14bf396451c623a36fa4bac6","tid":1880746,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"彭博：廁紙成香港貨幣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200215/DPVI4AS55LQ2O3SDY3W77P5CN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200215%2FDPVI4AS55LQ2O3SDY3W77P5CN4%2F&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNnejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=acc15ec4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200215%2FDPVI4AS55LQ2O3SDY3W77P5CN4%2F&h=ecc1f0bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200215/DPVI4AS55LQ2O3SDY3W77P5CN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n全球瘋搶 內地推口罩期權約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200215/large/1581696481_aa82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200215%2Flarge%2F1581696481_aa82.jpg&h=f88e7593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全球掀起搶購防疫物資潮，內地一間口罩專用物料供應商，獲免費提供一份認購期權合約。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎肆虐，掀起全球搶購防疫物資潮。山東一間口罩專用物料供應商，獲免費提供一份認購期權合約，可保障4.5億個醫用口罩或一億個N95口罩原料成本。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">彭博：廁紙成香港貨幣</span><br />\n<br />\n《證券日報》前日報道，山東道恩集團是口罩過濾層使用聚丙烯的專用物料供應商。在建行（939）總行支持下，建信期貨子公司建信商貿向道恩集團，免費提供一份行使價為每噸7,234.5元人民幣的PP2005亞式認購期權合約，規模為500噸，相當於保障4.5億個一次性外科口罩或一億個N95口罩原料成本。<span style=\"color: orange;\">據悉每噸聚丙烯約可生產90萬個單次使用醫用口罩或20萬個N95口罩。</span><br />\n<br />\n彭博昨以〈廁紙成香港新貨幣〉為題報道，<span style=\"color: orange;\">口罩與廁紙是香港和新加坡的財金界送禮首選，較萬寶龍鋼筆或真皮銀包更吸引</span>；香港對沖基金Solitude Capital創辦人兼投資總監Joel Werner指，近日見香港廁紙賣斷市，周一到亞馬遜網購216卷廁紙，單計運費也要200美元（約1,560港元），但他認為物有所值，形容「廁紙送禮，更勝紅酒」。<span style=\"color: orange;\">新加坡網上交易平台IG亞洲業務開發主管Terence Tan則指，公司為求吸客，向客戶派發3M N95口罩、電子探熱器及滴露消毒液。</span>"},{"pid":"5184080d0f7f97ac1d44ff23a0089e3b7a00497a","tid":1880746,"uid":58301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:48:49.000Z","msg":"Masks futures<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c0b21dbc08f91ade243284ff97025443030661","tid":1880746,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"無搶過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dfab70e92f92fdbc2d09386458b423115cdc3f","tid":1880746,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"多謝廢老，香港人形象又再低啲"},{"pid":"40a9369f29ae58a33deb2192b2cb582060495029","tid":1880746,"uid":89752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:57:57.000Z","msg":"搶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a890e6909479046680d02408cf95d1bbc77377c5","tid":1880746,"uid":278712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"金口罩，銀廁紙，銅搓手液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34db0b3c5e1db7d2ea254d45dc7e3795fee2fa4","tid":1880746,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vKY8IZGem6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvKY8IZGem6g&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNnejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=91e1f53b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vKY8IZGem6g</a>"},{"pid":"62a5f505e021b0f0703d25621e12e2b0b1e0d974","tid":1880746,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a890e6909479046680d02408cf95d1bbc77377c5","tid":1880